The Bank of Enlgand said it was creatingand taking onto its own books a one stg tranche of the nine pctExchequer stock due 2002.    The issue is part paid with 20 stg pct payable on issue andthe 76 stg pct balance due on April 27. First dealings willtake place this Wednesday, March 4.    The initial reaction among dealers was to mark pricesaround 1/8 point easier. The market had been untapped prior tothis announcement. REUTER&#3;